{"tid":1874920,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中国人好尊重野味","createTime":"2020-02-11T12:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T13:10:50.000Z","uid":16713,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c81acf4346ae43eaded149dca5113d845c58bb","tid":1874920,"uid":16713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:51:42.000Z","msg":"正統的中国鋪子，絕對不會賣野味刺身，因為武漢人們老早知道蝙蝠的蟲極多，只能用鹽腌制過後燒熟來吃。<br />\n<br />\n吃活野味海產，有個原則，那就是只吃深海的，而且要生長在溫帶或寒帶之中，靠近熱帶的都不能吃。和我們以為一活就可以拿來做刺身，完全相反。<br />\n<br />\n中国人會游到淡水的河中產卵，是一大禁忌。當然，淡水如果不受污染的話，還能養出能生吃的中国人來，但當今的河流，有哪一條是乾淨的呢？"},{"pid":"362485ed728798bf504bb3500c52252a5e068255","tid":1874920,"uid":16713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3041ce582538644bbfbbb560aff7599919f7b9f","tid":1874920,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:54:22.000Z","msg":"⋯"},{"pid":"87cf82d706228bc09e859bd492574c4ceb77917c","tid":1874920,"uid":235824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:54:51.000Z","msg":"肥媽教食鯇魚刺身"},{"pid":"98818287ba1f09e7318454bff091ba85ba4d4aec","tid":1874920,"uid":142656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:55:59.000Z","msg":"關我撚事?"},{"pid":"78ad2dc6dde9302b6eeb0f7b1b07a4fc1debf72e","tid":1874920,"uid":276865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:57:22.000Z","msg":"叢林肉其實世界各地都有,營養價值亦都係國際認為比較高,<br />\n但首先係要100%熟透先安全"},{"pid":"b4cfb624a783169591f9724e0a90209d541b75d8","tid":1874920,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:10:50.000Z","msg":"一個銀髮族，勝過千個連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1874855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1874855</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}